'''Willigis Jäger''' (born 7 March 1925 in [[Hösbach]]) is a German [[Order of Saint Benedict|Benedictine]] monk, [[mysticism|mystic]], and [[Zen master]], who trained and taught in the [[Sanbo Kyodan]] tradition (being given the Japanese name Koun-ken) until 2009, and then continued his own sangha independently.

